ed="T" n="0731b28"/><persName key="A009269">釋宗哲</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000004810"><placeName>西河</placeName><placeName>平遙</placeName></placeName>人也。稚歲而有奇相，聰頴<lb
ed="T" n="0731b29"/>天資，既尋師範，砥節飾躬。屬<persName key="A000294">玄奘<roleName>三藏</roleName></persName>新<pb ed="T" n="0731c" xml:id="T50.2061.0731c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0731c01"/>翻諸經論，<persName key="A009269">哲</persName>就其門，請益無替<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g522"/>，凡幾周星<ptr type="glossary" target="#g659"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0731c02"/>備窮諸典，若指于掌，於<persName key="A000294">奘</persName>門下號為<persName key="A009269">得<lb
ed="T" n="0731c03"/>意哲</persName>，猶<date from-iso="+0581-03-06" key="j19333311946884" to-iso="+0618-04-15"><name>隋</name></date><persName key="A004580">慧布</persName>之題目<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1243"/>焉<ptr target="#n660"/>。後因講唱，厥義<lb
ed="T" n="0731c04"/>日新，時謂之為「法江」。<persName key="A009269">哲</persName>曰：「為<ref type="person" target="#A009269">吾</ref>謝<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g661"/>此品藻<lb
ed="T" n="0731c05"/>焉，殊不知<ref type="person" target="#A009275">法海</ref>在乎<placeName key="PL000000003793"><anchor xml:id="beg0731001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>大</sic><corr>太</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0731001"/>原</placeName>矣。」所指者蓋<lb
ed="T" n="0731c06"/><persName key="A009275">浮丘</persName>為滄溟也<ptr target="#n817"/>。<persName key="A009269">哲</persName>憫<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g662"/>學者不達其意而師，<lb
ed="T" n="0731c07"/>誖哉，乃著義例，寰海之內莫不企<anchor xml:id="beg0731sgsz7"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>羡</sic><corr>羨</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0731sgsz7"/><ptr target="#n1087"/>。其如<lb
ed="T" n="0731c08"/>說「佛位三事喻」中，<persName key="A001708">沼<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>言「三點三目」<ptr target="#n663"/>，強<lb
ed="T" n="0731c09"/>分上下，勝劣配屬，太成巧誣。<persName key="A009269">哲</persName>云三事俱<lb
ed="T" n="0731c10"/>得。然無名師品量。退而省之，<persName key="A009269">哲</persName>其得矣。號<lb
ed="T" n="0731c11"/>之「<ref type="person" target="#A009269">得意</ref>」，豈虛也乎！<persName key="A001708">沼<roleName>師</roleName></persName>所以成餘師<ptr type="glossary" target="#g664"/>之說也。</p>
